data.description: Fantastic 3 Bed, 4 Bath Multi-Level home in popular Sunny Slope. Features a spacious 3 garage garage, neutral colors, soaring ceilings. Situated on a large 1/3 acre lot, the backyard is fenced w/ covered porch.  All new LVP floors in Liv. Room/Dining room. Eat-in kitchen w/ SS Appliances. Primary bedroom walks out to large Deck with amazing views to the East & no rear neighbors! Finished lower level has Rec room & addtl. 3/4 Bath. Close to interstate access and short walk to neighborhood Park/Pool!  AMA
